This strawberry watermelon smoothie is a delicious refreshing drink made with juicy sweet fruit. Watermelon goes well with a variety of fruits, including strawberries. It is filled with antioxidants from the strawberries, which is why this smoothie has many anti-inflammatory properties. Ingredients: Preparation: Step 1: Combine strawberries and watermelon in a high powered blender and blend until smooth. Step 2: Pour the strawberry watermelon smoothie into glasses and serve immediately.